{"tid":1770591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣新方向]天冷了，請多加休息","createTime":"2019-12-05T10:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T11:11:13.000Z","uid":17378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"615d3ccdd403d6e8e64d0193a83c30723138fb3f","tid":1770591,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉<br />\n<br />\n天冷易生病，被窩暖笠笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你知道嗎，多睡5分鐘，只能多休息5分鐘<br />\n多睡兩小時，卻可以休息一整個上午！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆不準時，是員工遲到的榜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當返工變成事實，生病就是義務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式罷工之前，將種種叫人射波嘅句子每朝spread比身邊親朋好友，潛移默化，鼓勵大家怒射佢老母，到真罷工嘅時候可以令人更易接受同埋實行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d21639d34f1ebdf9b4c17f9fc3bc8d1d40fb2e","tid":1770591,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"文宣師請出招"},{"pid":"cd97dddf1dc23ef2d969fb3cadf4887d97ffe8af","tid":1770591,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c6f2440da3c33843a774d24c5ce016161f4f2e","tid":1770591,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8290a508809623a15836df6f30b967b7ac234533","tid":1770591,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901d43f9e3882035ad1de1af80a12a6951a30870","tid":1770591,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:16:20.000Z","msg":"比我瞓多5分鐘"},{"pid":"928faf505a22e827e954c8d